nodes.text: Gold Two was the call sign of a clone trooper pilot who served in the Battle of Muunilinst. He took command of Gold Squadron after Gold Leader's death.

As the battle over Muunilinst began a huge number of Geonosian starfighters joined the battle, Gold Leader was killed while the rest of Gold Squadron was being decimated. Gold Two took immediate command after Gold Leader's death. After informing Commander Skywalker of enemy reinforcements coming from point 3 5, Gold Squadron was ordered to get out of there by Commander Skywalker.
